&lt;h1 id="original-2014-review"&gt;Original 2014 review:&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Out of all the pre-Avengers / &lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Marvel_Cinematic_Universe_films#Phase_One:_Avengers_Assembled"&gt;Phase One&lt;/a&gt; Marvel Cinematic Universe movies, it&amp;rsquo;s really a toss up whether Iron Man or Captain American was my favorite. In &lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Marvel_Cinematic_Universe_films#Phase_Two"&gt;Phase Two&lt;/a&gt;? It&amp;rsquo;s not even a question&lt;sup id="fnref:1"&gt;&lt;a href="#fn:1" class="footnote-ref" role="doc-noteref"&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;. Captain America: The Winter Soldier.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>